        :summary = "The Visible and Infrared Imager/Radiometer Suite (VIIRS) Primary Productivity product estimates net carbon fixation by phytoplankton in oceanic waters using the algorithm of Behrenfeld and P. G. Falkowski (1997) with chlorophyll a and Photosynthetically Available Radiation (PAR) values from VIIRS and Sea Surface Temperature (SST) values from the NOAA Gridded Super-collated product as inputs. The science quality chlorophyll a, SST, and PAR data are included in the dataset. Data are mapped to a NASA 4km Standard Mapped Image." ;
